---
const milestones = [
  { year: '2013', label: 'WANG Founded', detail: 'Girls\u2019 education, flood response & rural digital literacy in Balochistan' },
  { year: '2022', label: '50 Homes Rebuilt', detail: 'Sustainable housing for women-led families after Pakistan\u2019s mega-floods' },
  { year: '2024', label: 'Urdu AI Launches', detail: 'Grows to 1M+ community \u2014 the world\u2019s largest Urdu-language AI education platform' },
  { year: '2024', label: 'WIRE / MIT Solve', detail: 'Women-led social enterprise. 500+ women empowered. 2025 MIT Solve semi-finalist' },
  { year: '2025', label: 'PakSpeed Goes Live', detail: '15,000+ speed tests in Week 1 \u2014 Pakistan\u2019s first community-owned connectivity data' },
  { year: '2025', label: '5 Platforms, 35M+ Reach', detail: 'Urdu AI, PakSpeed, AI for Edu, AI Viewer & WANG/WALI \u2014 two continents, one mission' },
];

const credentials = [
  'Brandeis University (Heller School) \u00B7 Canadian Mennonite University \u00B7 University of Balochistan',
  'PM Youth Excellence Award \u00B7 ADB Climate Resilience Award \u00B7 British Council Global Changemaker',
  'Atlas Corps (U.S. State Dept.) \u00B7 Rise Up (Gates Foundation) \u00B7 DO School \u00B7 ISOC Fellow',
  'Only Pakistani org selected for Google AI Opportunity Fund: Asia-Pacific',
  'Funded by AVPN, Google.org, Internet Society & Asian Development Bank',
];
---

<section class="story section" id="story">
  <div class="story__inner container">
    <div class="story__left">
      <div class="story__left-sticky">
        <span class="eyebrow reveal">Story</span>
        <h2 class="story__heading reveal">
          The mission came first.<br />
          <em>The tech followed.</em>
        </h2>
        <ul class="story__credentials reveal">
          {credentials.map((item) => (
            <li class="story__credential">
              <span class="story__credential-mark" aria-hidden="true">&#9670;</span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story__right">
      <div class="story__narrative">
        <p class="story__paragraph story__paragraph--dropcap reveal">
          I came to AI through development work — not the other way around. After years studying how communities are shaped by systems of power and exclusion, I watched artificial intelligence become the most consequential of those systems. The question underneath all of my work has always been the same: who gets left out?
        </p>

        <blockquote class="story__pullquote reveal">
          <p>220 million people speak Urdu. Almost none of the world&rsquo;s AI education reaches them. So I built the infrastructure to change that.</p>
        </blockquote>

        <p class="story__paragraph reveal">
          Urdu AI grew into Pakistan&rsquo;s leading AI literacy platform — over one million people through social media, a weekly newsletter, a mobile app, and workshops across the country. The largest Urdu-language AI education community in the world, built without a venture round or corporate backing.
        </p>

        <p class="story__paragraph reveal">
          PakSpeed followed — because you cannot talk about digital inclusion without honest data on who actually has connectivity. Pakistan&rsquo;s first community-owned internet speed network logged over 15,000 tests in its first seven days.
        </p>

        <!-- Impact Milestones -->
        <div class="story__milestones reveal">
          <h3 class="story__milestones-title">Key Milestones</h3>
          <div class="story__timeline">
            {milestones.map((m) => (
              <div class="story__milestone">
                <span class="story__milestone-year">{m.year}</span>
                <div class="story__milestone-content">
                  <span class="story__milestone-label">{m.label}</span>
                  <span class="story__milestone-detail">{m.detail}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story__documentary reveal">
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F0aSyRMBrLE" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="story__documentary-link">
            <span class="story__documentary-badge">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"></polygon></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="story__documentary-text">
              <span class="story__documentary-label">Featured Documentary</span>
              <span class="story__documentary-title">Tackling Inequality Using the Internet — Internet Society (2023)</span>
            </span>
            <svg class="story__documentary-arrow" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M4 12l8-8M5 4h7v7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="story__paragraph story__paragraph--closing reveal">
          Different platforms. Different communities. One conviction: AI should belong to everyone who needs it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
